- winsock version: ctrl+c is not handled instantaneously, but only after an
  interruptible function is called in main loop (printf,login, etc)
 consequence: ctrl+c is only handled next time a client tries to log in

- after a kill the data connection of the killer seems corrupted:
---> SITE kill 16386
<--- 200 KILL signal sent
200 KILL signal sent
lftp pollux@localhost:/> ls
---> PASV
<--- 227 Entering Passive Mode (127,0,0,1,9,196)
---- Connexion du socket de données à (127.0.0.1) port 2500
---> LIST
<--- 501 No data connection available.
---- Fermeture du socket de données
ls: L'accès a échoué: 501 No data connection available.
lftp pollux@localhost:/> ls
---> PASV
<--- 227 Entering Passive Mode (127,0,0,1,9,197)
---- Connexion du socket de données à (127.0.0.1) port 2501
